'''阿提米絲2號'''（Artemis II）<ref>{{cite report|title=Artemis: brand book|location=Washington, D.C.|publisher=National Aeronautics and Space Administration|date=2019|id=NP-2019-07-2735-HQ |quote=MISSION NAMING CONVENTION. While Apollo mission patches used numbers and roman numerals throughout the program, Artemis mission names will use a roman numeral convention.}} {{PD-notice}}</ref>是[[NASA|NASA]][[獵戶座太空船|獵戶座太空船]]的首次載人飛行任務，目前計劃由[[太空發射系統|太空發射系統]]在2023年8月發射。<ref name="IG-20-018">{{cite web |url=https://oig.nasa.gov/docs/IG-20-018|title=Report No. IG-20-018: NASA's Management of the Orion Multi-Purpose Crew Vehicle Program|work=Office of Inspector General (United States)|publisher=NASA|date=2020-07-16|access-date=2020-07-17}} {{PD-notice}}</ref><ref name="SFN20200518">{{cite web|last=Clark|first=Stephen|url=https://spaceflightnow.com/2020/05/18/nasa-will-likely-add-a-rendezvous-test-to-the-first-piloted-orion-space-mission/|title=NASA will likely add a rendezvous test to the first piloted Orion space mission|publisher=Spaceflight Now|date=2020-05-18|access-date=2020-07-17}}</ref>目前的計劃是讓一艘載人的獵戶座太空船執行月球飛越測試並返回地球。這是自1972年[[阿波羅17號|阿波羅17號]]以來首次飛離[[近地軌道|近地軌道]]的飛行任務。

以前稱為'''探索任務2號'''（Exploration Mission-2,EM-2），該任務在[[阿提米絲計畫|阿提米絲計畫]]成形後重新命名。

